{"tid":832903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★首班即延誤　直達廣州南列車花近一小時 客一度鼓譟","createTime":"2018-09-23T06:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T07:59:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b1eddf698b00b2a5d123d720c7cc7db4c8d9f436","tid":832903,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180923/s00001/2e6a365eafe1dcd3521c7bc4bfbc5cac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180923%2Fs00001%2F2e6a365eafe1dcd3521c7bc4bfbc5cac.jpg&h=bb538317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府早前公布，由西九總站直達廣州南站的列車最快47分鐘，特首林鄭月娥昨日通車儀式時試搭，更稱43分鐘就到廣州南。惟《明報》記者今早乘搭早上10時由西九總站開出、不停站直達廣州南的首班列車，但花了53分55秒才到站，較政府公布的車程多接近7分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n此外，列車亦較原定時間遲了2分鐘開出，職員原本提醒乘客，會在開車前5分鐘停止上車，但記者乘搭的10時班次，最終在9時53分鐘才開始開放讓乘客進入月台上車，部分<span style=\"color: red;\">乘客一度鼓譟</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180923/s00001/1537675605533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180923%2Fs00001%2F1537675605533&d=vTi2tvMzgm8sWSCP0n%2FUbzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a0604baa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180923%2Fs00001%2F1537675605533&h=64b5ab2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180923/s00001/1537675605533</a>"},{"pid":"4318d930b47f30e13e25e9a92263f3d3ba4789e6","tid":832903,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b1852ddfa2e9e5e36bb1468017b1074612da19","